{"tid":2390282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸軍方稱將舉行自由公平選舉　把權力移交勝出的政黨","createTime":"2021-02-01T12:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T14:39:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"01252cf1fe2ad3a9c85e0f8407871b4943e04c5e","tid":2390282,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573503-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573503-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=e1c13cc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573503-20210201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fb2ff6d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573503-20210201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方表示，將會舉行自由及公平的選舉，將權力移交勝出的政黨。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸新的軍政府舉行會議後，在軍方網頁發表文章，表示國防軍總司令敏昂萊承諾，將以公平方式，實踐真正富有紀律的多黨民主制度。文章未有提及舉行選舉的具體時間表，但軍方早前頒布的緊急狀態為期一年。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸發生政變，軍方以回應去年大選舞弊為由，拘留國務資政昂山素姬及總統溫敏等領導人，並將國家權力已移交敏昂萊。全國民主聯盟以昂山素姬的名義發出聲明，指軍方的行動是要令國家重回獨裁統治，敦促民眾不要接受，應該抗議。"},{"pid":"ee2dab1b86ec3388e237231c3376004c38b9749f","tid":2390282,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"緬甸版dominion<br />\n選到贏為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e1598d6178a011bfa1184e7c47b4130113857c","tid":2390282,"uid":92125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"美國都應該咁做啦"},{"pid":"ccf7d828f058e3e4bc19cf1b07afcf1f24f23e51","tid":2390282,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"ON9"},{"pid":"bb2bda96fad156ec0a5feb5cf7a6025def6abd20","tid":2390282,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"同泰國一樣<img src=\"/as